<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style type="text/css">
    body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0 2vw;
        background-color: #f5feff; /* Light blue background for the entire page */
        font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
    }

    main {
        margin: 5vh 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    section {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        background-color: #f5f0e3; /* Soft yellow background for sections */
        border: 2px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 5px;
        padding: 20px; /* Increased padding for a book-like feel */
        margin-bottom: 20px; /* Add some space between posts and footer */
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); /* Add a subtle box shadow */
    }

    p {
        text-indent: 1.5em;
        line-height: 1.5; /* Improve line spacing for readability */
    }

    img {
        max-width: 100%; /* Allow images to span the width of the section */
        display: block;
        margin: 0 auto;
        border-radius: 5px; /* Add rounded corners to images */
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); /* Add a subtle box shadow to images */
    }

    pre {
        background-color: #333; /* Dark gray background for code blocks */
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 5px;
        padding: 10px;
        overflow: auto;
        line-height: 1.4;
        color: #fff; /* White text color for code blocks */
        font-size: 14px;
        font-family: Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace;
    }

    footer {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        font-size: 14px; /* Adjust font size for the footer */
        color: #555; /* Slightly darker text color for the footer */
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 767px) {
        body {
            padding: 0 2vw;
        }
    }

    @media only screen and (min-width: 768px) {
        body {
            padding: 0 15vw;
        }
    }
    </style>
    <title>dcdourado</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; margin-top: 5vh">
        <img style="width: 165px; height=auto; border-radius: 10%" src="assets/images/profile.png" />
        <div style="flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; margin-left: 5vw">
            <h1>Diogo Carneiro Dourado</h1>
            <h4>
                I am passionate about leveraging technology to improve people's lives.
                I began programming for enjoyment in 2009, creating scripts and websites.
                I graduated with a Bachelor's degree in Computer Engineering from the Federal University of Itajub√° between 2017 and 2022.
                Since 2019, I have been working professionally as a software engineer, gaining valuable experience at renowned organizations such as Stone and QuintoAndar.
            </h4>
        </div>
    </header>
    <main>
        <h1>Posts</h1>
        <%= post_callouts %>
    </main>
    <footer style="margin-bottom: 1vh">
        <span>Maintained by @dcdourado</span>
        <span>Find me on <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/dcdourado">Linkedin</a> and <a href="https://github.com/dcdourado">Github</a></span>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
